item.title: The Fascinating History of Magic through the Ages
item.description:
In today's episode, explore the fascinating history of magic, from its ancient roots in ritual and mysticism to its evolution into modern-day fiction and literature. Discover how magic has captivated audiences across cultures and centuries, blending mystery, philosophy, and religion.
